## Phase 2: Build User Management System

> New feature following `ARCH-01`, `ARCH-02`, `ARCH-REF-01` structure.

### users Feature (New â€” `src/features/users/`)

#### [NEW] `src/features/users/server/route.ts`
- Hono router with `verifyAuth` + `requirePermission(RESOURCES.USERS, ACTIONS.READ)` middleware (`FEAT-SERVER-01`)
- **`GET /`** â€” List all users with role, status, lastLoginAt (paginated)
- **`GET /:id`** â€” Get single user with role details
- **`PATCH /:id`** â€” Update user: `roleId`, `isActive` (deactivate/reactivate)
- **`DELETE /:id`** â€” Soft-delete by setting `isActive = false` (not hard delete)
- **`POST /invite`** â€” Create invitation using existing [createUserInvitation()](file:///c:/Users/HP/Documents/Next.JS/website/src/lib/rbac.ts#225-281) from `@/lib/rbac`
  - Permission check: `RESOURCES.INVITATIONS`, `ACTIONS.CREATE`
  - Sends invitation email via `emailService`
- **`GET /invitations`** â€” List pending/accepted/expired invitations
- **`DELETE /invitations/:id`** â€” Cancel a pending invitation
- All endpoints use `zValidator` with Zod schemas (`FEAT-SERVER-02`)

#### [NEW] `src/features/users/schemas/user-schema.ts`
- `updateUserSchema`: `z.object({ roleId: z.string().optional(), isActive: z.boolean().optional() })`
- `createInvitationSchema`: `z.object({ email: z.string().email(), roleId: z.string() })`
- `userQuerySchema`: pagination params + filters (role, status)
- `invitationIdParamSchema`: `z.object({ id: z.string() })`

#### [NEW] `src/features/users/types/user-type.ts`
- `UserWithRole`, `InvitationWithRole` type exports using Prisma types

#### [NEW] `src/features/users/api/use-get-users.ts`
- React Query hook: `GET /api/users` â†’ `UserWithRole[]` (`FEAT-API-01`, `FEAT-API-02`)

#### [NEW] `src/features/users/api/use-update-user.ts`
- `useMutation` hook: `PATCH /api/users/:id`

#### [NEW] `src/features/users/api/use-invite-user.ts`
- `useMutation` hook: `POST /api/users/invite`

#### [NEW] `src/features/users/api/use-get-invitations.ts`
- React Query hook: `GET /api/users/invitations`

#### [NEW] `src/features/users/api/use-delete-invitation.ts`
- `useMutation` hook: `DELETE /api/users/invitations/:id`

#### [NEW] `src/features/users/components/invite-user-dialog.tsx`
- Dialog with email input + role select (lists all roles from DB)
- Uses [dialog.tsx](file:///c:/Users/HP/Documents/Next.JS/website/src/components/ui/dialog.tsx), [form.tsx](file:///c:/Users/HP/Documents/Next.JS/website/src/components/ui/form.tsx), [input.tsx](file:///c:/Users/HP/Documents/Next.JS/website/src/components/ui/input.tsx), [select.tsx](file:///c:/Users/HP/Documents/Next.JS/website/src/components/ui/select.tsx) (`UI-01`)

#### [NEW] `src/features/users/components/edit-user-dialog.tsx`
- Dialog to change role and toggle active status
- Uses [dialog.tsx](file:///c:/Users/HP/Documents/Next.JS/website/src/components/ui/dialog.tsx), [form.tsx](file:///c:/Users/HP/Documents/Next.JS/website/src/components/ui/form.tsx), [select.tsx](file:///c:/Users/HP/Documents/Next.JS/website/src/components/ui/select.tsx), [switch.tsx](file:///c:/Users/HP/Documents/Next.JS/website/src/components/ui/switch.tsx) (`UI-01`)

#### [NEW] `src/features/users/components/user-table.tsx`
